"PWB:T005PW0006B-C" and "DAT:2012.09.03" appears to be :silkscreened on the main board in the [https://fccid.io/document.php?id=1894138 FCC photos]. :"S/N:PS051700", "T104PW0012-G", "V1.3", and "20121019" :is silkscreened on the [https://fccid.io/document.php?id=1894137 power board]. :A sticker with "UD216GIAM-DT", "(T0055046-G)", and "9/2012" :printed on it is affixed to the USB Flash module.
Default SSID pattern may be '''LINKING_XXXXXX''' :(upper case hex characters for the Xes). :Default credentials are per the FCC manual. :Possible 94:D7:23 OUI...
